<h3 id="recast-t-float-this" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#recast-t-float-this" aria-hidden="true">#</a> .<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Ray.recast" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">recast<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ( t : Float ) : this</h3>
