<h3 id="set-origin-vector3-direction-vector3-this" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#set-origin-vector3-direction-vector3-this" aria-hidden="true">#</a> .<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Ray.set" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">set<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ( origin : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vector3<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>, direction : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vector3<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ) : this</h3>
<p><a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">origin<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> - <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Ray" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ray<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>（射线）的<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Ray.origin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">origin<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>（原点）。
<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">origin<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> - <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Ray" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ray<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>（射线）的<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Ray.direction" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">direction<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>（方向）。 该向量必须经过标准化（使用<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector3.normalize" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vector3.normalize<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>），这样才能使方法正常运行。</p>
<p>根据参数设置该射线的 <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Ray.origin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">origin<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> 和 <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Ray.direction" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">direction<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> 。</p>
